            <abstract>
<p>The homily is devoted to the events surrounding Christ's resurrection. It displays textual affinities
  with <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1750LahaMa">Lāḥa Māryām</ref>. According to the
  colophon (e. g. in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFabb80">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien d'Abbadie 80</ref> the homily was translated into Gǝʿǝz by ʾabbā <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8387SalamaI">Salāmā</persName>.</p>
            </abstract>
